♫ <i>When I'm unaware</i> ♫

32
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:03,400
♫ <i>He always quietly appears</i> ♫

33
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:10,400
♫ <i>Why is it always he who stirs my heart?</i> ♫

34
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:13,800
From now on, you can always kiss me.

35
