♫ <i>I'm loving you</i> ♫

36
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:24,600
♫ <i>I really do</i> ♫

37
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:29,200
♫ <i>I want to get closer to you</i> ♫

38
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:32,000
♫ <i>Love should be cherished</i> ♫

39
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:35,200
♫ <i>I'm loving you</i> ♫

40
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:39,600
♫ <i>If you want me, too</i> ♫

41
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:43,700
♫ <i>Don't just stand there in silence</i> ♫

42
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:45,500
Drive.

43
